text: Unless u moving in with ur family.. sell old flat
He alone staying in 4 room flat??

My frd was helping me for like 1 year looking for houses but nothing was suitable. I wanted simei but simei prices are high.Then i met my bf…after a few mths i told him that i am looking (i scared) then he introduced his godsis to me and found my current house
Old flat can rent. Under parents name.
So i believe finding houses is fate…
My tenant told me if i ever want to sell my house  sell to him
Time to eat breakfast. I still lying on my bed.😂😂
I jiak bfast n nap liao  shower also
Waiting for nurse tell me can go 😁
Haven start i am perspiring liao
My home got 4 parcel to unpack 🤣
I didnt knw i hospitalised. All i put locker address
I notice aliexpress coins is useless. Waste my time check in everyday.
If only my shoppee coins worth this much.😁
More n more niao. Used to be 120 coins
Recently my shopee frds also damn nice. Inform me got shopee shake
Cos i got tell a few .. few times
End up eat lunch then go cos need order alcohol swab
Play game till doze off. Shiok to be in aircon
Of course Aircon always shiok de
I didnt shit ever since i come in 🫢
Aiyo keep asking doctor n nurse for med..dunno wth they doing. Say will give..no give till i going to discharge
I go bck drink kopi .... will detox
They beri beri slow de 🤣
I early morning drink ice Milo will detox
The pinoy nurse say  "hao liao" sounds like hello 😂
My mum will chase until they backside catch fire 🤣
Even now order alcohol swab need wait 1 hr 😵‍💫
Their accent 😂 very funny one
I lazy chase liao cos going to discharge
By right b4 lunch... now need eat lunch then go
Cos i dunno wait till wat time. Eat lunch first better
I still think of eat bfast set that toast
Later i eat lunch   see if my stomach got space bo 🤭
I am watching drama…now i watch china drama more and more
Dunno later still need go dwn collect med or not or can collect here🤔
Ding ² dong ². Smelly ² 1pm then can go 🤣
Actually I never watch one series of china drama 😅
Same same the timing my sister and mum discharge b4
And s2 of moon lovers coming this year 😍
This time round the emperor will come to the future to find IU lol
I got mc till next monday hmm
Sometimes go HK or Thai lakhon 🤣
Another one week no need move 🤣
